<br>
I chose agnostic, which has made the game easier but has screwed me cause no tunare armor for my HIE Mage.  So i'm assuming that limits me to Thurgadin or Dragon quests cause my velious giant faction is soooooooooooooo screwed hehe.<br>
<br>
Are there others?  what is the best for a mage to pursue? <br>
<br>
Thanks in advance<br>
 <p><br>Balas Fizilking -- Say hello to my little friend.

