s=title>   Re: Need some help with quest armor - Agnostic</span><hr size=1> The only people that aren't KoS to giants are Troll/Ogre warriors that worship Rallos Zek (this is what I've heard, not something I've tested myself).  While SS is better than Kael armor, it really comes down to what faction your guild chooses/has chosen.  The differences are pretty minor, though I'm glad I'm on SS cause it is slightly better for casters.  I'd go for apothic, and then save any gems you get for quest armor and save them for Kael/SS armor not waste them on Thurgadin.  Thurgadin is a minor upgrade to apothic, and its not worth it (imo) to get the gems for Thurgadin and then have to get them again for Kael/SS.  Especially if your guild is at the level of doing Thurgadin, you can just do PoG instead. <p>~~
